{"type": "article", "id": 27619, "title": "无线充电板", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123728JUpmMaY9SXoqrhZB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>我们拥有的电子产品越来越多，充电的方式却鲜有革新。这款名为 Energysquare 的充电板想让你收起杂乱无章的充电线，轻松地为多个设备同时充电。它采用传导式专利充电技术，使用的时候只需要将配套的便签条贴到设备充电口，再设备放在充电板上就会自动进行充电。Energysquare 不仅充电速度和普通的充电器相同，表面还使用了防水设计，即使不小心沾到了液体也不用担心。如果你对它感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/700146891/energysquare-always-stay-charged\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 59 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123726lcynNojPQvVkHAdU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123727iJoWO8Z4etVgdNsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57584683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123727eioFfbc1a5rXs7gW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123727Q2xF5qfKABLMsXpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}